│ checking that when we have a valid element in the CommonMask (I2 !=         │
│ PoisonMaskElem), the corresponding element in the SubVectorsMask (I1)       │
│ should be PoisonMaskElem (-1), indicating it's unused. However, in our      │
│ case, we have overlapping non-poison elements between the two               │
│ masks.\n\nFrom the debugger output:\n- CommonMask = {-1, -1, -1, -1, -1,    │
